                            <td>Web Developer</td>
                            <td>2018-2020</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>Company B</td>
                            <td>Senior Developer</td>
                            <td>2020-Present</td>
                        </tr>
                    </table>
                    
                    <h3>Hobbies</h3>
                    <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Qui voluptatem quaerat ullam vel laborum sapiente magni natus quasi, animi accusantium deleniti cum est beatae, numquam alias vitae explicabo officia quisquam repudiandae optio mollitia voluptates.</p>
                    
                    <h3>Interests</h3>
                    <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Integer nec odio. Praesent libero. Sed cursus ante dapibus diam.</p>
                    
                    <h3>Skills</h3>
                    <div class="skills">
                        <span class="skill-tag">JavaScript</span>
                        <span class="skill-tag">Node.js</span>
                        <span class="skill-tag">Express.js</span>
                        <span class="skill-tag">MongoDB</span>
                        <span class="skill-tag">HTML</span>
                        <span class="skill-tag">CSS</span>
                        <span class="skill-tag">React.js</span>
                        <span class="skill-tag">Git</span>
                        <span class="skill-tag">Agile methodologies</span>
                    </div>
                    
                    <h3>Ratings</h3>
                    <div class="rating">
                        <p><b>Overall Rating:</b></p>
                        <div class="stars">
